title: Dead or Alive - Last Round Updated DLC 17/06/2015
description:
About This Game Experience the intuitive fighting system, gorgeous characters
and blockbuster stages of Dead or Alive 5 in this definitive series
finale!Two new playable characters join to make 34 fighters - the largest
roster in series history!Master the signature DOA fighting system through the
rich story and tutorial modes, unlock more costumes than ever before in each
of the offline training modes, and compete with the best fighters in the
world in the full-featured online training modes. Fight as ninjas, assassins
roughnecks & wrestlers as you knock your opponents off an exotic waterfall
into an exploding oil rig and more!The final word in fighting entertainment
Dead or Alive 5 Last Round!

on Steam.Thank you for your understanding!Online modes for Dead or Alive 5
Last Round will be added in a patch within 3 months of release
